            <p><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Coffee: it’s an essential and sometimes necessary part of many college students’ daily lives. As someone who usually sticks to drinking strictly tea </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">(</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">no offense), I’ve always wanted to know what makes coffee better and how to make it best. Because of this, I’ve decided to test some theories with an experiment. </span></p>
<div id="attachment_86538" style="width: 970px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-86538" data-attachment-id="86538" data-permalink="https://dailynexus.com/2019-02-27/hot-or-not-and-how-hot/a515f562-cd38-46c9-aaca-00e446a1dcbf/" data-orig-file="https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/A515F562-CD38-46C9-AACA-00E446A1DCBF.jpeg?fit=960%2C612&amp;ssl=1" data-orig-size="960,612" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta='{"aperture":"0","credit":"","camera":"","caption":"","created_timestamp":"0","copyright":"","focal_length":"0","iso":"0","shutter_speed":"0","title":"","orientation":"0"}' data-image-title="A515F562-CD38-46C9-AACA-00E446A1DCBF" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/A515F562-CD38-46C9-AACA-00E446A1DCBF.jpeg?fit=250%2C159&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/A515F562-CD38-46C9-AACA-00E446A1DCBF.jpeg?fit=888%2C566&amp;ssl=1" class="size-full wp-image-86538" src="https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/A515F562-CD38-46C9-AACA-00E446A1DCBF.jpeg?resize=888%2C566" alt="" width="888" height="566" srcset="https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/A515F562-CD38-46C9-AACA-00E446A1DCBF.jpeg?w=960&amp;ssl=1 960w, https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/A515F562-CD38-46C9-AACA-00E446A1DCBF.jpeg?resize=250%2C159&amp;ssl=1 250w, https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/A515F562-CD38-46C9-AACA-00E446A1DCBF.jpeg?resize=768%2C490&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="(max-width: 888px) 100vw, 888px" data-recalc-dims="1"><p id="caption-attachment-86538" class="wp-caption-text"><i>Courtesy</i> <i>of</i> <i>pixabay</i>.<i>com</i></p></div>
